<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>HYMN FOR LAUDS OF PENTECOST</B></FONT></H2>
<H3><PRE>
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Day of immense joy
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    in the city of God;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    may the flame of the Spirit 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                  Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    shine in the Cenacle.
                                 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  The wondrous gift of the prophets 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    is renewed on this day 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    and a mystic rapture 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    touches tongues and hearts.
                                 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Day of immense joy
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    in the city of God;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    may the flame of the Spirit 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                  Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    shine in the Cenacle.
                                 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  O blessed season 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    of the new-born Church,	
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    who welcomes in her womb 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    the first fruits of the nations.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Day of immense joy...
                                
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  This is the jubilee
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    of the fiftieth year 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    that ransoms the slave
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    and proclaims forgiveness.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Day of immense joy...     

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Send upon us, O Lord,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    the gift of your Spirit;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    grant to this restless world 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    justice and peace.
                                 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am              G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Day of immense joy...

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Light of eternal wisdom,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    reveal to us the mystery 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    of the one and threefold God,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    fountain of eternal love.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    G Am                             
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Amen.
</PRE></H3>
